      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Tricky race but GODDESS OF ROCK (3) is in great form and should go close again. Forgive the run two back when bombed the start but atoned last time with a determined win. Up a little in weight but returning career best figures lately and expected to measure up again. FLORENCE GLASS (2) scored back to back wins before a close-up fourth behind GODDESS OF ROCK latest. Meets her slightly better at the weights and can turn the tables. HAPPY CLAN (1) was runner-up in the same race and is overdue for a win, but gets no weight relief for the winner. Going well though and should be in the finish. ALWAYS A WINNER (4) is building to a win and looks one of the chances. NATIVE CLAN (5) is overdue and should be thereabouts.",
